infoparam.value:
Incoherencies 1. The Controller block interacts with all sensors and actuators but lacks a direct relationship or interaction with the User, which is crucial for the system's functionality as described in the use case diagram. ->OK (ControlConsole)
2. There is no explicit block or signal representing the system's ability to 'Maintain_Position_And_Course' as described in the use case diagram. -> Partial OK (system_operation_status has been added)
3. The DPS block is isolated without any relationships described, which does not align with its intended role as the central system integrating all functionalities. -> OK
4. The attributes of the Control Console and DPS suggest some redundancy (set_course/set_position vs. desired_course/desired_position) without clear distinction or interaction. -> OK New signals and attributes
